!= css('listen')
!= css('chat')
h2 Songs on Screen
h5.smallhideme with Sam and Peter
p(class="{{muting}}", ng-click="muteme()") mute
div(scroll-glue, class="well chatbox")
    div(ng-repeat="chat in chats")
        div(ng-switch="chat.type")
            .chatitem(ng-switch-when="chat") <b>{{chat.speaker}}</b>
                span.says {{chat.content}}
            .announce(ng-switch-when="announce") {{chat.content}}

form(class="navbar-form")
    input(type="text", placeholder="Chat about the show", class="input-block-level")